{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_208","type":"agent_message","text":"`akka.util.Reflect.findConstructor` uses `Class.getDeclaredConstructors()` and filters the result at runtime. That means constructor discovery needs a query-capable registration, not just an invokable `<init>` signature, so I’m patching the `Guardian` type accordingly."}}
